in government, you might have thought that

39
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:18,850
the decision was actually a good decision
at the time it was made, and if you were driving

40
00:03:18,849 --> 00:03:22,739
and looking in the mirror so you could make
a turn, you might have not seen the pothole

41
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:26,469
yourself.
So don’t be that annoying person who feels

42
00:03:26,469 --> 00:03:31,479
