don’t blame others for something that seems

44
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:42,530
so obvious just because it’s already happened.
Of course it’s obvious now, but it wasn’t

45
00:03:42,530 --> 00:03:48,560
obvious before it actually happened.

46
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:53,870
So the 3 big ideas are…
1. Priming. Realize the power of even the

47
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:58,039
